title: LFP - Plat 5 Jg main Looking for Duo Partner
body:
Hi I'm plat 5 currently, with my peak being plat 2. I consider myself higher skill level than plat 5. I main jungle: shaco, kha'zix, fiddlesticks(actually + win-rate and great at fiddlesticks) (mid fizz secondary). 
Looking for a partner of any lane.
Please add: Somatomax if interested
